{"tid":1042212,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打試過喺gogogo退票？","createTime":"2019-03-01T11:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T15:47:11.000Z","uid":9629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9ee4e5b58e8d9cd693a83eed0bf07fad2cd25f","tid":1042212,"uid":9629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T11:48:00.000Z","msg":"上年9月買左機票諗住去玩下<br />\n點知因為山竹去唔成就退票<br />\n<br />\n佢地嘅員工就話退票要4至6個月<br />\n我等到依家都仲未退到錢（仲有兩個星期就6個月啦）<br />\n<br />\n早兩個星期打上去問下<br />\n佢地話要check下條數返左未<br />\ncheck到依家都未check到<br />\n開頭話等幾日，之後會覆返我但係都無覆過我<br />\n次次都要自己打上去再問<br />\n次次都係叫我等多幾日係咁拖<br />\n（我已經等左幾次幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果航空空司退左錢俾佢地<br />\n佢地唔係應該盡快退返比我咩<br />\n點解到我打上黎你先同我check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想快啲退返啲錢返黎都咁難咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴打試過類似經歷？<br />\n可以做啲咩令佢地可以快小小退到錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab9aebd0f76ebd56e7614a4f94fb12016d8f2db","tid":1042212,"uid":9629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:04:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5f9f4e3399dad44533989c3a4cc0002a28f9ed","tid":1042212,"uid":9629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9ca1ca7ec45797bef9f22b8c65194950502855","tid":1042212,"uid":9629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fbb95249e505895790d729ea547b69437fefb4a","tid":1042212,"uid":9629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:41:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58cb704cafb29fc532f115cf7706d31ad18c85d7","tid":1042212,"uid":9629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T13:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e23fd0ef6cc4f409adc113a4cec7e2414e9855","tid":1042212,"uid":9629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55709be31be7379408df9922971495c2b8f99949","tid":1042212,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:47:11.000Z","msg":"on9去中介買機票"}]}